eater understanding in this transformed global environment.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aMiddle East Studies. 4aPolitics -- International Relations. 4aSecurity Studies -- Middle East Security. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Globalization.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476715640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767156423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767156/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles